            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is cooked through, transfer the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board, reserve the tray[s] and shred apart using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Separate the <strong>roasted onion</strong> into petals – these are your <strong>tandoori-style onion petals</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1667320657763-x200.jpg",
